ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>生物齒輪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n創造者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登無神論者已潛入老母個臭閪到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\non9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人腦結構比起齒輪精密一百倍添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYes, 生物學裏面神經傳導都係透過正負高低電位差黎傳導訊號，電子學都係一樣。"},{"pid":"6f68d949ea22054514ccb8445df7a5d0527fb82e","tid":154409,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T11:29:54.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"772dd57e7549b58070ddfa5d0002e280c928ca14","tid":154409,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:14:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>.</blockquote><br />\n你係老母個臭閪到出返黎未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}